{"tid":1244932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［飛機po］Sing Hallelujah 之621心法","createTime":"2019-06-20T06:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T06:26:02.000Z","uid":264029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3c67a459134f1069324d64a41f3ee9d6b8b400c2","tid":1244932,"uid":264029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:26:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 殊途同歸</span></span></strong><br />\nSing Hallelujah唱分部有先後開始地點，<br />\n音有高低之別，但係同一首歌！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">解：</span></span></strong><br />\n目標一致，訴求清晰！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">各施其職，不分化不割𥱊！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 保持儆醒</span></strong></span><br />\n唱耐咗會甩beat會變調會發呆<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">解：</span></span></strong><br />\n敏感身邊發生嘅事，唔好鬆懈！<br />\n天氣好路線好地形好裝備好，做好加密措施，同內心預備worse case scenario。<br />\n唔洗中無謂伏/伏隊友。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Take care Good luck !</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 心中有&ldquo;神&rdquo;</span></strong></span><br />\n唱詩歌係要知道自己係人，面對住自己嘅信念<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">解：</span></span></strong><br />\n只有&ldquo;神&rdquo;先可以判定人心，其他人點睇點鬧都無傷肝。<br />\n按自己所持嘅良知思考同行動，不自大/ 自限<br />\n有人就救人，有需要就去做。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>4. 兄弟手足</strong></span></span><br />\n你停底飲水冷靜，會有人接到唱下一句<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">解：</span></span></strong><br />\n因為有人，件事先會work！<br />\n彼此照顧，因為我哋經歷緊同樣嘅痛苦，擁抱同樣希望。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>5. 重覆至成功</strong></span></span><br />\n唱十次唔得，唱到廿次總會識唱<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">解：</span></span></strong><br />\n要堅持、忍耐，保持鬥心<br />\n我哋未贏，但係做啱嘅係要一直堅持，即時眼前冇效果<br />\n如果唔係等於否定自己個夢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">最緊要有HP，就有機會！😭</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 歷史最終係屬於我哋香港人！</span></strong><br />\n一首沖涼嘅時候諗到，Minor調嘅讚美歌，相信包括作者自己都冇諗過，宇宙會咁樣用佢<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">解：</span></span></strong><br />\n冇論你做衝，二線，物資，救護，出計，文宣，地鐵嗌咪，派傳單，同廢老對話，教細路，祈禱，外交，自我修煉乜乜乜<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港歷史都會有你參與！！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n識唱嘅心裡面一齊唱！<br />\n<br />\n分久"}]}